snippet.title: Among Us: Hide N Seek Official Trailer | The Game Awards 2022
snippet.description:
Don't be Sus! Amogus is back with more content. This time, Among Us revealed an all new mode - one where a player controls a clear and obvious monster for Hide N Seek. Among Us Hide N Seek releases December 9, 2022.

#amongus #thegameawards #gaming
